recipe_name: Chia Coconut Pudding with Coconut Milk
ingredients: 2 cups sweetened coconut milk, 6 tablespoons unsweetened coconut milk, 1 tablespoon agave nectar, or more to taste,   +   1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract,   +   1/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon, 1 pinch salt,   +   1/2 cup chia seeds,   +   1/2 cup diced fresh strawberries (Optional)
nutrition: Total Fat 22g 29%, Saturated Fat 17g 87%, Sodium 40mg 2%, Total Carbohydrate 11g 4%, Dietary Fiber 5g 19%, Total Sugars 3g, Protein 4g, Vitamin C 11mg 53%, Calcium 83mg 6%, Iron 4mg 22%, Potassium 237mg 5%
